      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DOONGALLA SERENA (1) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by 2.75 lengths at Bendigo in a handy 28.19 beating Urana Orbit. Draws the cherry and has the ability and in winning form. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Expected to be right there at the finish again. NOSEY BLUEY (5) finds it hard to break through. Has hit the frame at his last three runs, the latest finishing second (29.78) at this track. Has a good record at this journey. Hard to beat again. DR. WARREN (3) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (32.93) at Traralgon behind Dr. Paris in a Restricted WIN. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Expected to feature again. I'M EASY (4) should be thereabouts.",
